{
  "stem": "2067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Her premonitions as a-- as a woman usually has-- were better. 1942 came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And early in 1942 came the yellow star the Jews had to wear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We started preparing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We don't-- we didn't live at home anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had an address with a gentile woman in the western part of Amsterdam, which is for the work-- workmen part of Amsterdam-- lower-- lower income class.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We entered a room there and slept there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We only came out for a few hours to visit either my parents or his parents, and-- and [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Dottie. ?] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the noose became tighter and tighter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the 5th of July 1942, I was just coming home, going back to my apartment from [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dottie's. ?] I saw the mailman going up the steps to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said where does the Ringel family live?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said I am one of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He handed me a card, a special delivery card.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That special delivery card said, it came from the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are herewith ordered to appear on I believe it was July 10th at 8:00 PM in the evening at the central station of Amsterdam to be sent to a labor camp in the east-- or Germany.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Max had established before that time a relationship with a Dutch gentleman, a stockbroker, a wealthy gentleman who had a house in the center of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the first floor was the-- his business-- stockbroker business with several employees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The second floor he had the-- he was the general secretary of the church-- the schools of the reform church in the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were several employees on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the third floor were his living quarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
